
   ABILITY:  intimidate <player>
   LEVEL:    Racketeer
   COST:     Low graft

   DESCRIPTION:
     Force <player> to fork over some cash.  If the player
     denies payment, you will both be taken to a sparring
     room where you can rough the player up and teach 'em
     a lesson.  Players who continually ignore your intim-
     idation tactics may have a contract put on their life.
     NOTE: Players that have paid protection will not be
     affected by this ability.  See 'mhelp protect'.

